  "text": "Researchers have introduced a number of optimizations for S-BGP [CITATION_1] , mainly focusing on caching signed and verified routes and applying DSA pre-computation. These optimizations reduce the computational cost related to cryptographic operations, in exchange for extra memory cost and computation complexity.",
